queries.sql: SELECT `supplier`.*, GROUP_CONCAT(karyawan.nama_lengkap SEPARATOR ", <br> ") as admin, GROUP_CONCAT(users.id SEPARATOR ", ") as id_admin FROM `supplier` LEFT JOIN `supplier_penanggungjawab` ON `supplier`.`id` = `supplier_penanggungjawab`.`id_supplier` LEFT JOIN `users` ON `supplier_penanggungjawab`.`id_user` = `users`.`id` LEFT JOIN `karyawan` ON `users`.`id_karyawan` = `karyawan`.`id` WHERE `supplier`.`deleted_at` IS NULL GROUP BY `supplier`.`id` ORDER BY `supplier`.`id` DESC
